comment:
I had hopes when you stated that's things started to get crazy, but still nobody wants to say a word about any culpability Depp may have for taking shit loads of illicit drugs and alcohol in close proximity with his wife, who was taking medication for mental illness in Australia, at least, in the absence of other information; after he chose to marry, at the age of 48, the 23 year old adolescent, let alone the Hollywood team that worked so hard to cover up the domestic violence in Australia. It takes much less bothersome thinking to totally condemn and cancel the problematic Heard. what should be done, should she be hung like Epstein? and that does not require answering for those who don't understand rhetoric when they see it.
The tapes only reveal certain timeframes and Depp is a consummate actor, but please understand I am not accusing him of playing for the tape only stating a possibility.
Everyone just loves to judge, maybe because understanding involves self reflection.
I lived with a beautiful talented high achiever who was the most charming man whom I loved all my life, but he had a nasty nasty side that he never allowed himself the space to deal with, very few are total psychopaths, maybe Heard is, I don't have the evidence for that especially as the bad behaviours can not be separated from the implication f drugs and Hollywood, we have to draw strict boundaries and forgive and severely sanction those who strongly prove their malevolence.
I am not a Christian but; hate the sin not the sinner. If anyone bothered to read through this please understand I am not judging Depp, or Heard, at all, just speaking as someone who has experienced at least one somewhat similar relationship and have been responsible for harmful behaviour myself, as happens when we are overly selfish. I seem to have finally found a path to recovery and am able to forgive my perpetrators(most) as people, but do not give a pass to the system that allows and even at times facilitates abuse, as I try to forgive my self for my failings in the path and strive to move forward to a space where others don't suffer awfully from the shit in my head that only I can sort out, with the help of others who have true knowledge of the mind and a will to help people actually untie what binds them to ignorance and fear, not just to control and sell us empty promises in the form of products.
No-one is innocent in this sad, widely syndicated type of 'marriage' toxic, whatever the details. Anyone with self respect, required if we are to be able to respect other, would likely have left literally before the honeymoon was over, if even making the decision to make their way to the alter. and this is not victim blaming, only holding people responsible for themselves, as well as calling out the corporate system that apparently denied these 'superstars' a opportunity for getting meaningful help and more timely justice.
